1. SmuggleFuzz

Description: SmuggleFuzz, a configurable and rapid HTTP downgrade smuggling scanner. Empowering users with customizable gadget lists, it offers deeper insights into the reasons behind failed smuggling attacks. I am confident that numerous HTTP downgrade-based smuggling vulnerabilities remain undiscovered. Unfortunately, many individuals cease their exploration after a cursory scan. By using SmuggleFuzz, you can uncover smuggling vulnerabilities that others may overlook.

ToolLink: https://github.com/moopinger/smugglefuzz


